column4: Morning woke up was tough. I would most likely continue sleeping. I need to go to the bed earlier today to sleep little bit longer. #n #xfb
Walk to train station wasn't so bad and hurry today. It's raining today a bit, but nicely. What matters I forgot the breakfast. #p #xfb
What a good status. We were laughing a colleague about lobby for the new feature. I look forward to have Madeleine for breakfast. #p #xfb
Redrawing the design description diagram. It's complex, but I like it, while it helps me to explain the problem to others. #p #xfb
Working and my wife disturbs me with her research about bicycles. I don't want to choose right away I need to read about it first. #n #xfb
Finishing drawing and looking forward for lunch. I need to rewrite text in document to be aligned with picture and it's finished. #p #xfb
And now after really good lunch I want to sleep or at least rest for a while and have something sweet like blueberry muffin. #p #xfb
Returning to work through discussion with colleague of his problem and meanwhile responding to questions about living in Swiss. #p #xfb
Passionate discussion about really interesting work topic inside team. Conclusion is known, but discussion is going on and on. #p #xfb
Almost forgotten to write my tweet during discussion with colleague of mine. But besides that I solved with him one more problem. #p #xfb
Starting to get tired today already. It's too much things which I need to focus on, discuss, handle, take care of. Better be 5 pm. #n #xfb
Little break and few minutes of walk help to refresh my mind, I am back on the track again and ready for meeting in next 15 minutes #p #xfb
When the team leader tells you at the beginning of your presentation: it's bullshit. There are no arguments. Except it was good joke #p #xfb
Meeting ends with funny topics. It's time to close it and go home. Finally. But there is still lot of to do on the table. #p #xfb
Leaving home. What a relief. I need to enjoy the sunny weather and the family. There is expecting me the good meet for grill. #p #xfb
Back at home. Going to prepare grill and relax. It's nice to do nothing and just sit and have clear mind and no chaos around. #p #xfb
Enjoying dinner with my wife on balcony with kids on the grass outside. I have delicious black Angus steak and chicken pieces. #p #xfb
I smell by smoke from grill so I need to go to the shower before I will go to bed watch some series or work. #n #xfb
Choose a bike is not easy I am little bit in depression what parameters to care about and what brand to choose I need to take a time #n #xfb
Finished by bike selection I am going to find some episode to watch and relax. Bikes available in CZ are not available in Swiss, wtf #n #xfb
Watching TV show and relaxing with popsicle in bed. Wife is still continuing with bicycle research. I am enjoying the show. #p #xfb
The Simpsons at the end of the day are the best. We are enjoying it both And I will go maybe work after instead of sleep right away #p #xfb
Kicking trough usage of @fitbit API library from @github, so far it's going well. Right now I need to test OAuth to my application. #p #xfb
My heart beat is like I would run the race. But what helped to have nice woke up was daughter who came to visit us in our bed. #p #xfb
Waiting for the train and trying to call back on my colleague missed phone call. It could be about pizza order I hope not work. #p #xfb
Guys already ordered pizza for me what a pleasant surprise. Fuck I am late for my meeting from nine o'clock. I need to run. #n #xfb
Passionate discussion with important people. There are topics which cannot be discussed just once I think. Never ending story. #n #xfb
Sitting on the meeting with explosive topic and waiting when the fight start. So far we went through surprisingly smoothly. #n #xfb
Going to be hottest with explosive topic. But meeting is almost over. I am really interested if there would be decision or not. #p #xfb
I will starve to death if the time would not run faster and lunch would not be here as soon as possible, yesterday was too late. #n #xfb
Pizza with ham and pepper and strawberries as desert is my dream lunch. It's getting to be better and better. #p #xfb
Siting on the terrace with ice cream and relaxing for a while before I return to the lion pit downstairs. I need to finish some work #p #xfb
Doing company expense report from last month. I don't like it but it has to be finished today since it's almost half of actual month #n #xfb
Currently is much piece full time I can finally work on my tasks without so much disruption I hope I have at least one hour to do so #p #xfb
Finishing iExpense and discussing several things around. I am little bit nervous about how much we need to finish till end of Sprint #n #xfb
I need to say it's really difficult to keep on track with work in such difficult customer environment like here and do experiment. #n #xfb
I thought that updating existing process would be easy but it cannot be more far from true. I am close to finish and go home. #p #xfb
Few more things has to be finished. I need to adjust design picture about one small part and then publish it for everyone. #p #xfb
Finally waiting for the train home. I even printed some birthday party invitations with Frozen theme. Let's see what girls will say. #p #xfb
Having for dinner tasty goulash soup and relaxing through reading advertising flyers from many grocery stores. #p #xfb
My wife is referring me about news and I am looking for some episodes for watching during today evening. #p #xfb
What to watch next. Maybe How to get away with murder? From typical series there is nothing new broadcasted yet. We need to wait. #n #xfb
Wau subtitles for episode of blacklist are ready. Let's watch it and enjoy it. What a nice relaxing moment in the middle of the week #p #xfb
My wife has blocked neck and thus terrible headache and it seems that pain killers doesn't work for her. I hope it starts soon. #n #xfb
Painkillers helped a bit she can go sleep. I hope it will be better. Meanwhile I am continuing with get data from @fitbit #p #xfb
And it's last tweet today. My wife sleeps and I can continue to work. It's good except I am not successful yet, but it comes soon. #p #xfb
Tough woke up. I would sleep one or two hours more, but it's not possible But extended weekend with free Monday is closer and closer #p #xfb
It's rainy day hallelujah it's rainy day hallelujah, sarcasm! Sort of raining. And train is about few minutes late. Nice combination #n #xfb
It looks like today will be another hectic day as usual. Many things which I need to care about I hope I have time for my work. #p #xfb
Finally working on my own tasks not solving someone's else problems. And listening really good Czech songs. Pleasure. #p #xfb
Slowly fixing the issues and thinking about many things have to be done. And people around are asking me questions about their work. #p #xfb
Many funny situations about which from all 8 environments is used for what and by whom. But release manager seems to be in picture. #p #xfb
Busy with lunch and after explanation of situation about the team and project to still new member of the team. At least he knows #p #xfb
Things are not going anywhere. The solution is not difficult, but implementation is lions pit or walk through the hell. #n #xfb
Many new information and messages made my day. Best is that someone else point them out so I am not the one who points the finger. #p #xfb
Progress is going forward. I have solved one problem but turned into another one so still is what to do to achieve final test. #n #xfb
Cannot fix the problem. Google doesn't help and I cannot get any idea how to solve it better on target side. I need to change source #n #xfb
Skipping the overall project status meeting and continue with work. Going to test several other options. I am not sure if this helps #n #xfb
Slowly finishing the work and looking forward to leave to company office drop there expenses. Family pick me up at the there. #p #xfb
Ran to the tram which is leaving in 2 minutes. Currently my heart is running the race and I cannot catch the breath. #n #xfb
Back at home. My wife look better today even though she has still blocked neck it's not that bad as yesterday I guess it's good sign #p #xfb
Helping colleague with overnight load of 1300 tables with few TB of data. It's like before plain departure, we need to do checks #p #xfb
Little stress situation some tables which should be loaded are missing. Trying to call colleague but he doesn't respond. #n #xfb
Eating pizza and watching various TV shows at @streamCZ. And finally relaxing with my wife in the bed after really long day. #p #xfb
Watching another episode how to get away with murder. Eating strawberries, peaches, apricots and resting. #p #xfb
Kids are in their beds and we are continuing to watch TV show. They want us to sleep with them which is sweet. #p #xfb
Watching the third TV show and have taste for something, something good. So Iva went for something and brought kitkat and watermelon #p #xfb
Just checked load and because of missing tables in source it crashed. Colleague created ticked about it and we can go sleep. #p #xfb
Playing logical game with name rop and slowly preparing for sleeping. Tomorrow is last though day of the week and then 3 days off #p #xfb
Beautiful morning when my daughter came to our bed to woke us up gently. And it's just today and then three days off. #p #xfb
This morning train which always go few minutes before mine and goes through the station without any speed decrease is terrible. #n #xfb
Standing on standup meeting and listening to status of work from my colleagues. Meanwhile I am preparing for what I will do today. #p #xfb
It's becoming funnier and funnier here. Another team have poor performance on their scripts, but complain about database feature. #n #xfb
Project organization becoming more and more chaos since we are closer to go live. We need to keep it organized at inside team. #n #xfb
I have been successful with problem solution, so I just need to test it on several small and big cases before I can release it. #p #xfb
I have really good lunch crispy duck with gnocchi and wine source. And as a desert watermelon and strawberries. #p #xfb
Discussion after lunch about political incorrect topics related to project without any members from other teams we call blackops. #p #xfb
System is slow because is really occupied by many tests and runs. So, I need to do several things in parallel to stay busy. #p #xfb
Solved critical point with missing space in database that was the reason of failed load. So, we can continue with load. #p #xfb
Tried to continue of massive delta load test with colleague, it's not possible because latest deployment package is not deployed yet #n #xfb
After last hour of hurry is situation in open space calming down and we are on the track again. This chaos is really exhausting me. #n #xfb
I had really interesting discussion about nice core database automatic deployment and currently I can return to my original work. #p #xfb
Listen 7 Years song from @LukasGraham on YouTube and slowly closing work to be able go home. I would need to just check the load. #p #xfb
Finally waiting for the train and looking forward to have some good dinner and watch some good movie together with my wife. #p #xfb
I am at home, sitting on the couch and relax with rop game. I am challenged by little bit difficult round, but whatever. #p #xfb
I had several toasts for dinner with really good dressing and then I did research about sources for sentiment unsupervised learning. #p #xfb
Currently I am searching for some move for Friday night. Meanwhile my wife went to laundry room to pickup the laundry. #p #xfb
Keep the tweeting time schedule is really hard. So, sometimes the second alarm makes me realize that I forgot to write previous one. #n #xfb
Watching nice movie Brooklyn with my wife. And relaxing in the bed. After movie I need to check load if still running ok. #p #xfb
After we returned from laundry room and we watching excellent movie Brooklyn. Despite almost no story it's wonderfully shot. #p #xfb
Raspberries with white yogurt and hint of  sugar is really tasty late dinner especially in combination of such movie as Brooklyn #p #xfb
Watching The Big Bang Theory for the good night, after good movie little bit fun. Then I will continue work on @fitbit data. #p #xfb
Morning is better than night. Daughter doesn't feel well so we need to take care about her and we went sleep at four in the morning #n #xfb
I need to sleep at least one hour more, because of the occasion in the night. So far kids sleep as well so it's perfect. #p #xfb
Filip woke up already and brought the big box of Lego with him to living room and since then he plays, he said he is not hungry #p #xfb
Chocolate Brioche and then yogurt with banana and raspberries is tasty breakfast for today. After we need to go grocery shopping #p #xfb
Noon shower is really good idea it woke me up completely and recharged me by new energy. I am feeling like newborn. #p #xfb
Meanwhile the @fitbit was charging we were watching with kids dancing #stormtrooper group on @YouTube who are really amazing. #p #xfb
Find a place to park a car in the shopping center when is raining is not task for human. Especially in here in Switzerland. #n #xfb
Waiting in the line for taking foto with bear. After we passed the eye test in optic shop. What a wonderful day with family. #p #xfb
Testing perfumes in Douglas we need to renew our collections at home People in the office can expect perfumed man on Tuesday morning #p #xfb
Paying the grocery and finally going home from the overcrowded shopping mall. I am starting to have headache from the noise. #n #xfb
I just finished the storage of grocery into kitchen and I need to eat something and then we can prepare late lunch or early dinner. #p #xfb
Pork meat si prepared and sliced and part of the potatoes as well, we need more so I am going to pick some in basement. #p #xfb
Dinner cooks and we are relaxing by watching Charlie Chocolate Factory movie. Really magnificent one which kids loves. #p #xfb
Dinner is almost ready and soon the movie ends as well, so we could go eat. And I am little bit tired because I haven't slept much. #p #xfb
Dinner was excellent. We are going to pick up laundry and then relax with movie Bridge of Spies into bed. Kids watch Inside Out. #p #xfb
After first twenty minutes the story starts to be more interesting. Kids are noisy a bit and my wife is sleeping. #p #xfb
Chatting with father in law about possible Skype call between grandmother and kids and planning it for tomorrow or Monday. #p #xfb
Eating leftovers from dinner and taking the kids to beds. I will sing them song for good night and let them sleep. #p #xfb
Movie went into most interesting phase. Maya came to our bet to calm before she will go sleep. And we are relaxing. #p #xfb
We took Maya back to her bed and found something good for eating, delicious chocolate bar. And we come back to watch the movie. #p #xfb
I wrote email to bank about ownership of our property and currently return to work on getting data from @fitbit API. #p #xfb
Maya came to woke me up with words: daddy woke up it's morning already. But I don't want to come out from warm bed. It's too early. #n #xfb
I have prepared breakfast for Maya she wanted cereals with milk. I am slowly weaking up. Seems to be that today is not raining. #p #xfb
My wife made for me really good breakfast for me. And right now she is making a fun from me about tweeting so much. #p #xfb
Cleaning up the apartment and sorting out the things. My wife is running around clean and order and yelling on all of us. #n #xfb
I am vacuum cleaning the bedroom and sort out the papers. I don't like it, but it was necessary due to lot of dust around. #n #xfb
We are preparing lunch. We need to go with Maya to balcony cut rosemarine, she likes to help Iva searches for kitchen tools for kids #p #xfb
Chicken legs on garlic and rosemarine are in owen and I can mount the magnet on doors for garbage bin. And then I can rest. #p #xfb
Magnet on the doors to garbage done. And chicken pieces are baking. Iva is going to prepare rice and I can finally relax. #p #xfb
Filip sitting on my lap and feed me his chocolate chips cookie. What a pleasure afternoon. We will go walk to forrest. #p #xfb
We are looking at the old photos because Maya wanted to see her self small and remember to the old times. She is amazed. #p #xfb
Ready to go out to forrest. Kids are playing with tennis ball which I have found in my bedside table hidden from them. #p #xfb
Finally out. Kids are singing two different songs and I am singing third one it's perfect disharmony, but we have lot of fun. #p #xfb
We found in the forest two in love snails. Kids are amazed. And we all are enjoying the fresh air and silence around us. #p #xfb
Just right now talking over Skype with my parents. Kids stayed just for fits few minutes and then disappeared to play along. #p #xfb
Family is currently calling with mother and father in law and I am cleaning computer from personal stuff because I will get new soon #p #xfb
Having a dinner a tousts and kids are watching story tale Planes 2. Then we go to bed watch some series or movie as well. #p #xfb
We have 2 Broke Girls and Arrow for watching so relax can start. With also two toasts with apricot marmalade. Good evening. #p #xfb
Watching Iva how she is playing game INKS and download several episodes of previous mentioned series. Kids are movie ends soon. #p #xfb
Relaxing and thinking about what to do after the shows ends. If to follow up with @fitbit API or to work about the 100 jobs load. #p #xfb
Still relaxing with the movie. It's really exciting, but it is end of the episode unfortunately it's not the end of the story #p #xfb
@fitbit was trying to wake me up for fourty minutes even though I woke up already and tried to convince it I am awake. #n #xfb
I will sleep at least till next alarm clock. Today is bank holiday so, no rush no hurry. We will play with @Mindstorms_EV3. #p #xfb
Finally I am leaving the bed. It was terrible morning but I hope it will be nice day. Despite the weather outside is rainy. #p #xfb
@fitbit thank you, finally I know how to kill the alarm. It will not disturb me any more in the morning. #p #xfb
It's holiday and everything is closed so we went to Coop Pronto on the gas station to buy toast bread and then walk through village #p #xfb
And we are back at home. I am looking for ebook for Maya who want to learn read and then I will grill spareribs for lunch. #p #xfb
Maya starts slowly to learn reading. She found out that's not easy and she won't learn read during one day. So, we can expect fight #p #xfb
Meat is prepared so I can fill in grill with coal and light it up and then the real fun starts. I am interested about the spareribs. #p #xfb
Sun is shining and I am on the balcony with beacon spareribs and chicken on the grill. Family cannot wait for it how hungry they are #p #xfb
Spareribs were not finished so I put it into owen and finish it when we are back from hiking through forest where we are going now. #p #xfb
We are in the forest and beautifully raining. We are going forward and enjoying the beauty of the nature, except the kids. #p #xfb
We are out of the forest in the grill place where are still firing embers in the fireplace. It's pleasant warm for our hands. #p #xfb
Kids don't want to take down the clothes and go to shower it's typical for every day agenda, but finally they are in the shower. #n #xfb
I have finished the spareribs baked in the owen, we have watched x factor gold buzzers and emotional moments. #p #xfb
Watching another episode Game of Thrones together with my wife, eating strawberries with hint of sugar. What a excellent evening. #p #xfb
So far a current episode is not such dark as some previous ones, but I am expecting more blood and violence soon as usual. #n #xfb
My wife has come with idea to follow the latest #luxusnataliri on @streamCZ, because she got a taste for the desert, so we made it #p #xfb
After spareribs for dinner, then strawberries with hint of sugar and finally for late dinner Czech dessert from apples and brioche #p #xfb
After another good episode of Game of Thrones we are watching How to get away with murder great TV show which is heading to the end. #p #xfb
We won at #Ricardo table which satisfies my wife and I hope it's heavier than current one which is moving whenever somebody touch it #p #xfb
And this is the last tweet for today. And not because my wife start to following me on Twitter, but because it's midnight. #p #xfb
Today was really bad woke up after not complete five hours of sleep I woke up in hurry situation where we need to go to municipality #n #xfb
The fact that I have to gave away my driving license to exchange it for the Swiss one is driving me crazy. Now I have just paper #n #xfb
After daily status I am listening the webex meeting about Running Hadoop proof of concept. I am really interested what is this about #p #xfb
Continue listening webex meeting and meanwhile solving the problems connect to my daily agenda and long term tasks. #p #xfb
Discussion of testing went to good direction. We matched most of the errors with logged details just few of them are missing. #p #xfb
Discussion of source metadata capturing with colleague is really thrill. But it ended with mutual consumption, so good day today. #p #xfb
Having a grilled chicken for lunch with my team leader and chief architect. And also blueberry muffin as desert afterwards. #p #xfb
Returned back from lunch and terrace coffee with colleagues. We had a really good discussion about how to good developers no need QA #p #xfb
Preparing of the tests objects for load test and listening various Czech artists. It's really calm down day no chaos no hurry. #p #xfb
I found error during generation of objects for testing. One of the objects wasn't generated at all. So, issuing ticket for fixing. #n #xfb
Had small talk about colleague who worked over weekend and came by Tesla S to work. Maybe some day I will buy one as well. #p #xfb
Found rejected expenses for no reason, told to project manager and he asked me to resubmit it, weird. Anyway system is rejecting me. #n #xfb
Switch to test another functionality which I have developed and currently not finished part I switched off to be finished next time #n #xfb
In hurry to finish test as soon as I can and family can pick me up from the work. I still have 40 minutes to do that. #n #xfb
Test load screwed up, so I am investing it on detail level. Data seems to be messed up in the source, so most likely not on my side. #n #xfb
Everything fixed, retested and functional. Also exported and committed for deployment, so I can finally go home and relax today. #p #xfb
I am at home, family picked me up at train station. And showered the kids and I am going to eat something for dinner. #p #xfb
Kids are watching the story tale and every preparations for tomorrow are done. So, I can download something for us. #p #xfb
Watching stupid girls in the new episode of Darwin prices at @streamCZ and eating strawberries and finally relaxing. #p #xfb
Watching How to get away with murder and meanwhile Filip cannot sleep so he visits us and telling us the story about skeletons #p #xfb
Watching @TheSimpsons in Paris, magnificent episode I need to say. My wife already sleeps because she had rough day today. #p #xfb
It seem that I cannot find #python #twitter API which either woks or has reasonable documentation. I need to try harder. #n #xfb
Maybe #tweepy looks that it should work. Question is how difficult is to get all necessary data from it. I hope it is not. #p #xfb
I can't kick myself from the bed. Listening voices from the kitchen where my wife and daughter speaking about kindergarten. #p #xfb
I missed the train just before my nose. So, I need to wait for another one and take it by longer way to the work today. #n #xfb
Sitting on the place and working. I returned to the task from yesterday. It's stressful topic since there is no solution yet. #n #xfb
I just discussed with my sister the summer holidays. I am looking forward for summer. Have 3rd assignment finished and no stress. #p #xfb
Looking for solution through adjustment of source of data so I can store it clean up and don't struggle with it in target. #n #xfb
Eating pizza and enjoying the lunch I need to take a break on the terrace later on with something sweet to have energy for meetings #p #xfb
Returned back to the computer. Trying new approaches before I will have 2 hours meeting marathon. #p #xfb
Right now planning the next sprint of our project with my team leader. It is necessary to clean it up and proper. #n #xfb
Discussion about company and it's current direction and what we expect from it. It's interesting discussion about interesting topic #p #xfb
Sitting on the terrace and having good conversation with my team leader about common stuff from our lives and thoughts about career #p #xfb
I have return back to the work. I helped to colleague to fix his problem which he was struggling with last hour. Second time today. #p #xfb
Struggling with different encoding conversions and characters representation and I cannot figure it out how to deal with it. #n #xfb
I am on my way home. I hope I was successful with the solution of the problem, but test on three object passed, so far so good! #p #xfb
We had a really good dinner and then I tried to read for kids the German book about princess Maja and right now relaxing on balcony. #p #xfb
We have found the bicycle in front our house for free so I took it to the basement for repair to be used by kids. #p #xfb
We are back from round walk through the village and close neighborhood and I am waiting till kids take of the clothes to get shower #p #xfb
I read the story tale #lichozrouti and it seems they like it a lot, they cannot stop. We can continue tomorrow for today it's enough #p #xfb
Watching magnificent episode #jidlosro about #granmoravia at @streamCZ. Then #varimesmirou which is more and more terrible. #p #xfb
Chatting with one of few best friend on @Skype about his paragliding course and making plans about alpine hiking trip. #p #xfb
We are watching #Bones the latest episode and the scene where Hudgins melting down the victim is magnificent and we saw it twice #p #xfb
I need to say that writing every day more than 20 times a day for every 45 minutes one tweet is hard work. So far I missed just few #n #xfb
My girls waving me for good morning, but just shower helped me to fully wake up to the new rainy day. I thought is Friday, but not #n #xfb
Somebody is smoking weed directly at the train station, no problem at all. I haven't running to catch the train today. #p #xfb
Daily status is behind me. Yesterday solution works just for part of the cases. Trying to come with something else. #n #xfb
Training Code of conduct is behind me. I don't know more boring training than this one, but what can I do when it is mandatory #n #xfb
Replaying to many JIRA issues and discussing colleagues problems to support them and technically lead them. Typical daily routine #p #xfb
Almost ready for the lunch. Seems to that I have to ask about advice from college about this problem with characters replacement. #p #xfb
Sitting in cafeteria and having good conversation with colleagues and relax after really good lunch. #p #xfb
@fitbit is there a possibility to improve water resistance of Charge HR by use plug into charge connector or is the button problem? #p #xfb
Excited, it seems to like the solution works even for such cases where it doesn't before. And moreover I got Swiss driving license. #p #xfb
Solution works except one record in small table and three big tables tests are running right now. I can continue with something else #p #xfb
During tables load and I am little bit bored. Here is hashtags explanation p is pos, n is neg sentiment and xfb is eXperiment FitBit #n #xfb
Table load crashed because not enough space in DB, so I cleaned it up and restarted. Right now I am sitting on weekly status meeting #n #xfb
Meeting is going to the end, so I will check the load and maybe I will go home today as I have planned let's see what else comes. #p #xfb
Waiting for the train and think about I have to finish fitness wristband market research to have an idea which one to buy next. #p #xfb
Preparing potatoes for garlic soup. I wanted to listen music, but BT speaker from @Bose has problems with charging and doesn't work. #n #xfb
Meanwhile the soup is boiling I have a time for snack before dinner. Yesterday Chilli con Carne with wholemeal toast is delicious. #p #xfb
Watching #blacklist episode and it's full of many twists. Enemies are working together and plan is changing the plan #p #xfb
Another episode How away with murder is better and better, I am really interested to which way the story develop. #p #xfb
Eating sweet frosting together with raspberries and blueberries with my wife in bed during watching series and relax. #p #xfb
Filip came to talk to us how he cannot sleep and he was sweet. He should sleep already because he had kindergarten today afternoon. #p #xfb
Finished with watching I need to work on my assignments a bit. But today not over midnight, because I need to sleep sometimes. #p #xfb
Preparing statistics for morning status and I have run the 9 hours taking job. When I am finished I will play with #fitbit API #p #xfb
This is last tweet for today and I am going to sleep. Totally tired all set and done and I can continue tomorrow morning. #p #xfb
Went sleep earlier than usual was good idea. I am feeling better, not fully rest yet, but better, fresh. And it's Friday! #p #xfb
Today I am at the train station little bit earlier than usual. Maybe I am looking forward for Friday and following weekend. #p #xfb
Eating breakfast the wholemeal buns with red oranges juice. It was time because I was starving during daily status meeting. #n #xfb
Stressful situation around, many people wants many things simultaneously. And I am trying to respond on shity email from testers. #n #xfb
Checking the emptiness of delta load and after I drunk juice I feel bad from stomach. Today is weird day, thank God is Friday. #n #xfb
Watching internal company knowledge call about Python language introduction. I am interested what new I will learn. #p #xfb
Eating good lunch with colleagues and discussing the painful issues which don't bother us, because we ignore them. #p #xfb
After return from lunch and desert on terrace the release manager jumped on my back and forcing me to help him with delta load. #n #xfb
Solving the issue with delta load which is working but loading nothing. The problem seems to be in the source database. #n #xfb
Let's see if I have at least little bit time for myself own work today. And also got information about some processes from college. #p #xfb
Got description of process from college as scatch on paper and going to property document it. Expecting leave work soon anyway. #p #xfb
Just walking home that would be big surprise for my family to see me home such early. I need to eat some snack and go inline skating #p #xfb
We are in the car and going to inline skate or bike to the lake. Family is excited I need to find the parking place. #p #xfb
We are riding inline skates. Maya is holding me tight because she is trying it fifth time in her life, so she needs to learn. #p #xfb
Waiting for the burger near the like. Filip decided that he wants to buy some food, because his belly is hungry. He has ice cream. #p #xfb
Maya is trying really hard to learn skating on inline skates. And I am solving some minor work issues via SMS with my team leader. #p #xfb
We have finished nine kilometers on inlines and Maya was magnificent because she mostly made it by her self and she must be tired. #p #xfb
Shopping #pombars because kids were excellent. And some apricots, blueberries and cheese to the grill. It's just a small purchase. #p #xfb
